Design Analysis


Constants

MTS - play area
HEIGHT - screen height
WIDTH - screen width

TANK - tank image
ALIEN - alien ship image
BLASTER - blaster shot from tank

TANK-Y - tank's Y position
ALIEN-X-SPEED - alien speed in X direction
ALIEN-Y-SPEED - alien speed in y direction

BLASTER-Y-SPEED - speed of blaster shot from tank


Variables

BLASTER-X - blaster x position
BLASTER-Y - blaster y position

TANK-X - tank x position

ALIEN-X - alien ship y position
ALIEN-Y - alien ship x position

Big Bang options

to-draw
on-tick
on-key
stop-when
